{"segment":2,"line_start":91,"line_end":180,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xu_xian","speaker_name":"徐先","listener":"char_jing_jun","text":"荆副统领是否准备再接受挑战？","tone":"疑问","chapter":156,"line_start":116,"line_end":117},{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_xu_xian","text":"刚才一场只是代统领出战，小将希望见好即收，以免给人轰出场去。","tone":"调侃","chapter":156,"line_start":118,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_xu_xian","speaker_name":"徐先","listener":"char_jing_jun","text":"副统领辛苦，休息一下吧！","tone":"欣慰","chapter":156,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"今晚看来管中邪不会再出手，因为只要他没有击败荆俊和你，在旁人的心中他始终不是最佳的剑手。","tone":"沉声","chapter":156,"line_start":130,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_wu_shu","speaker_name":"乌舒","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"齐人正收拾行装，准备远行。","tone":"焦急","chapter":156,"line_start":134,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"让二哥去吧！你留在这里应付吕不韦的阴谋。","tone":"沉声","chapter":156,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"吕不韦虽抽调不出人手护送田单离开，可是田单现时兵力达四千之众，与我们的总兵力相若，但若要对付高陵君，我最多只能分一半人给你，在这种情况下，说不定两方面均不能讨好。别忘了吕不韦有八千家将，谁知道他会干出甚事来？","tone":"无奈","chapter":156,"line_start":160,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"事情仍未绝望，我要去说服太子丹，只要他肯设法在楚境缠上田单十天、半月，我们便可赶上他，安谷傒曾答应过会把楚人和齐军逼离边界十多里的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":156,"line_start":166,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_tai_zi_dan","text":"田单不死，贵国才真正危矣。我并非要太子的手下正面与田单交锋，只要在田单离开秦境后，设法把他缠上几天，我便可及时赶去。","tone":"淡然","chapter":156,"line_start":176,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_tai_zi_dan","speaker_name":"太子丹","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"此事我们不宜直接插手或单独行动，一个不好，齐、楚两国会借口联手对付我们，三晋又分身不暇，我燕国危矣！","tone":"无奈","chapter":156,"line_start":172,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_you_zhi","speaker_name":"尤之","listener":"char_tai_zi_dan","text":"此事该有可为，只要我们采取设置陷阱和夜袭的战略，使田单弄不清楚我们是否项统领方面的人，那就算田单侥幸脱身，也不会想到我们身上。","tone":"陈述","chapter":156,"line_start":184,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_xu_yi_ze","speaker_name":"徐夷则","listener":"char_tai_zi_dan","text":"没有跟踪项统领的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":156,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_tai_zi_dan","speaker_name":"太子丹","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"好！我们设法把田单与齐军或楚人会合的时间拖延十天，若仍不见项统领到，只好放过田单。","tone":"认真","chapter":156,"line_start":190,"line_end":192}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xu_yi_luan","name":"徐夷乱","alias":[],"identity":"太子丹部下将领","faction":"燕国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"太子丹的部下将领，将配合尤之前去拖延田单","personality":{"traits":["武艺精湛","忠诚可靠","善战","果断","沉稳","服从命令"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"稳重"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_tai_zi_dan","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"服从"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[156],"source_refs":[{"chapter":156,"line_start":180,"line_end":182,"text":"我会派人随太子的手下去与贵属徐夷乱会合"}]},{"id":"char_xu_yi_ze","name":"徐夷则","alias":[],"identity":"太子丹部下将领","faction":"燕国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"太子丹部下将领，负责报告追踪结果","personality":{"traits":["沉稳可靠","善于侦察","忠诚","果断","谨慎","尽职"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"稳重"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_tai_zi_dan","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"服从"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[156],"source_refs":[{"chapter":156,"line_start":188,"line_end":188,"text":"这时大将徐夷则进来道"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_zhou_zi_huan","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":156,"line_start":108,"line_end":112,"text":"周子桓既惭且怒，又感气馁...发觉正好头额贴地"}]}}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":181,"line_end":262,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_guan_zhong_xie","speaker_name":"管中邪","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项大人，真不好意思，她说约了你在初更见面，却估不到你会早来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":156,"line_start":234,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_guan_zhong_xie","text":"害得管大人不能尽兴，还吓了一跳，该我陪罪才对。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":156,"line_start":238,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_guan_zhong_xie","speaker_name":"管中邪","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项大人尚未见到吕相吗？我来前他正遣人寻你呢！","tone":"疑问","chapter":156,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_guan_zhong_xie","text":"我正四处游逛，怕该是找不到我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":156,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_guan_zhong_xie","speaker_name":"管中邪","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"秦女婚前随便得很，项大人不会介意吧！","tone":"低语","chapter":156,"line_start":246,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_guan_zhong_xie","text":"管大人说笑了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":156,"line_start":250,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_guan_zhong_xie","speaker_name":"管中邪","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"那就顺道去见吕相吧！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":156,"line_start":254,"line_end":254}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ying_ying","name":"嬴盈","alias":[],"identity":"女儿军成员","faction":"秦国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"女儿军成员，与项少龙和管中邪均有情感纠葛","personality":{"traits":["开放大方","感情多变","美貌","善交际","柔弱","易受诱惑"],"speech_style":"温柔","temperament":"柔弱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"暧昧"},{"target":"char_guan_zhong_xie","type":"恋人","intensity":60,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被引诱"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[156],"source_refs":[{"chapter":156,"line_start":198,"line_end":200,"text":"记起嬴盈的约会"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
